<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n10137g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10137g">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10137g"> 137(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> tongues</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Le culte de Mercure n&apos;avait rien de particulier, sinon qu&apos;on lui offrait les <mark>langues</mark> des victimes, embl&egrave;me de son &eacute;loquence. <font color="green">[The cult of Mercury had no specific features, except that one offered to him the tongues of sacrificial beasts, emblems of his eloquence.]</font> <small> P. Commelin, <a name="NMGR" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#NMGR"><cite title="source">Nouvelle Mythologie</cite></a> (1907) 60</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
